```{.r .cell-code}
# install.packages("ggplot2")
library(ggplot2)

# Parametric equation for the heart shape
t <- seq(0, 2 * pi, length.out = 1000)
x <- 16 * sin(t)^3
y <- 13 * cos(t) - 5 * cos(2 * t) - 2 * cos(3 * t) - cos(4 * t)

heart_data <- data.frame(x, y)

# Plotting the heart
ggplot(heart_data, aes(x = x, y = y)) +
  geom_path(color = "red") +
  coord_equal() +
  theme_void()
```
